quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  60,1,"Eehey mon goon…óin…ďe wote njaggire a√Ī…ďe Mi e a√Ī…ďe mon heet…ďe ho…óon mberlo e mum en gilli te ko…ďe yeddu…ďe goongo gar…óo o e mon, ho…ďe njaltina nelaa…óo e onon sabu tan on ngoon…óanii Alla joomi mon, tawde on njalti sabu jihaadi e laawol Am e …óa…ďjude weluya am, ho…óon cuurtana…ďe kabaruuji juul…ďe ngam …ďe mbele mon, Mbe…óa anndi ko cuu…óoton e ko …ďanngi…óon, kala e mon ba…ó…óo …óuum o majji laawol peewngol"
  60,2,Si…ďe peewnatiima e mon …ďe ngOnana mon a√Ī…ďe …ďe mberta juu…óe ma…ď…ďe e …óem…óe mum en e mbaadi mbonndi …ďe nji…óiina nde ngonaton heeferee…ďe
  60,3,Nafatah on en…óameeje mon wonah …ďi…ď…ďe mon √Īande darnga O seernda hakkunde mon Alla na yi*a ko golloton ko
  60,4,"Woodanii on √Īeemtinirde mo∆ī∆īere e Ibraahiima e …ďeen wondu…ďe e mum nde …ďe mbi*i pellet ko min his…ďe e mon e ko ndewaton ko wonah Alla ko, min njeddii on fee√Īi hakkunde men nga√Īngu e tikkere haa pooma haa ngoon…óinon Alla gooto O, si wonah konngol Ibraahiima wonande baaba makko pellet ma mi yaafnano ma, mi alanaama hay huunde ka Alla, joomi amen min mbakkaliima e Ma ko e Ma min ndutti e ko e Ma woni wattande"
  60,5,"joomi amen wota wa…ó min fitina wonande …ďeen yeddu…ďe, yaafa amen joomi amen pellet ko aan woni teddu…óo mbo fooletaake √Īee√Ī…óu…óo"
  60,6,"Woodaniina mon e ma…ď…ďe √Īeemtanirgal mo∆ī∆īal wonande oon joortii…óo e Alla e √Īalngu laakara, oon …óuurnii…óo noon Pellet Alla ko gala jettaa…óo"
  60,7,"Yaama nde Alla wa…óata hakkunde mon e …ďeen …ďe nga√Īandir…óon gilli, Alla ko kattan…óo Alla ko kafroowo bakkatuuji jurmotoo…óo"
  60,8,Alla ha…óataa mon …ďeen …ďe ka…ďaani e mon e diine …ďe njaltinaani mon e galleeji mon nde …óigganton…ďe nuun…óon faade e ma…ď…ďe pellet Alla ko ji…ó…óo nuun…óu…ďe
  60,9,"Kono Alla ha…óata mon ko …ďeen ha…ďatoo…ďe mon e diine yaltinoo…ďe mon galleeji mon …ďe mballandiri e yaltinde mon, nde keetnaton …ďe kala ba…ó…óo …ďe keeda ko …ďeen ngoni too√Īoo…ďe"
  60,10,"Eehey mon goon…óin…ďe si goon…óin…ďe rew…ďe ngarii e mon njaribee…ďe Alla na anndi iimaan mum en, si on nganndii ko…ďe goon…óin…ďe wotee nduttee…ďe e heefer…ďe …ďe ndaganaaki heefer…ďe …ďe heefer…ďe …ďe kadi ndaganaaki …ďe, tottee…ďe ko…ďe nafqi ko bakkaat alah e mon nde ndesaton …ďe si on tottii …ďe teŇče ma…ď…ďe wote nanngite pi…ďle rew…ďe heefer…ďe naamnee ko nafqu…óon kam…ďe ne yo …ďe naamna ko …ďe nafqi ko, ko …óuum woni √Īaawoore Alla hakkunde mon Alla ko gannda √Īee√Ī…óu…óo"
  60,11,Si huunde faatiima mon e rew…ďe mon faade e heeferee…ďe leptu…óon …ďe tottee …ďeen …ďe rew…ďe mum en njahi fotde ko…ďe tottirno kulee Alla mbo goon…óin …óon O
  60,12,"Eehey ma annabi si rew…ďe juul…ďe ngari e ma ho…ďe coodandira e ma nde …ďe ndenndintah Alla e hay gooto,ngujjatah, njinatah, mbaratah sukaa…ďe mum en,ngaddatah fenaande fepindaande hakkunde juu…óe mum en e koy…óe mum en,…ďe ngoopataa Ma e mo∆ī∆īere ndeen de soodandir e mum en, yaafnano…ďe Alla, pellet Alla ko jaafatoo…óo jurmotoo…óo"
  60,13,"Eehey mjon goon…ói…ďe wote keetne yim…ďe …ďe Alla tikkani e dow mum en, …ďe pi…ďtiima e laakara hono no heefer…ďe pi…ďtari e yim…ďe genaale"